title: Launch Button does nothing
body: Keep pressing the Launch button and it doesn't go into the game. Sometimes it brings up the user agreement, but it never goes beyond that. Tried deleting and changing a few things, but it does nothing.

replies.body:
I have the same problem from the DJ Sona patch. Click launch, makes the sound, on rare occasions and after hours of trying it lets me in
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=idzspmlb2Mw
I've been getting the same problem since yesterday (Windows) , when I uninstall it, It does the same thing again, I've sent a ticket and let you know what happens next.

No, I'm on Windows. I can get on after a while (if it works), just takes ten minutes or so. But most of the time it doesn't get through.

It is a new pc (just got it the other day), so made sure I have Adobe Air installed and junk. Could be something else?

You don't need to worry about installing other softwares before installing League, as League will install any and all required software during its first boot.

Have you done your first update on your machine yet?
Messaged support, told me to make sure it was running under admin privileges, and that I should check my drive for errors, which i doubt because it won't work on both.
